work (CDN)<\\/a>&nbsp;such as caching and utilizing parallel downloads, you\'ll notice a&nbsp;huge difference in how fast your files show up on your page.<\\/p>\"}}},\"12\":\"The modern web is rich with photography, iconography, and video, but image-heavy sites can result in poor performance for the end user.\",\"13\":\"1\",\"16\":[\"16\"],\"19\":\"This is something\",\"18\":\"Hosting Static Files with S3 & CloudFront\",\"2\":\"\",\"20\":[\"6\",\"7\"],\"17\":[\"14\"]}}', '2017-02-22 21:54:22', '2017-02-22 21:54:22', 'e7d04f2a-b851-42ba-a41d-bc0846986e89'),
