INSERT INTO `craft_matrixcontent_bloglayout` (`id`, `elementId`, `locale`, `field_mainTitle_mainTitle`, `field_secondTitle_secondTitle`, `field_textBlock_textBlock`, `field_photoBlock_caption`, `field_quoteBlock_quote`, `field_quoteBlock_cite`, `dateCreated`, `dateUpdated`, `uid`) VALUES
 ('1', '5', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, '<p>The modern web is rich with photography, iconography, and video, but image-heavy sites can result in poor performance for the end user. Part of providing an elegant user experience is asset optimization, and we use Amazon\'s <a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/s3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">S3</a> and <a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/cloudfront/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">CloudFront</a> to do the heavy-lifting.</p>\n<p>There are a few reasons why we choose to use S3 to host static assets for our clients</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-21 22:37:07', '2017-02-22 23:05:26', '09197047-711a-4dce-8fb7-7118183b418b'),
 ('2', '11', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, '<p>Following our Design on Tap event, we chatted with Eric Steen, and Bruce Kehe, from Hopworks Urban Brewery about branding beer.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-22 16:15:31', '2017-02-22 21:30:40', '3925b2e6-a9fe-49bc-b7dd-8c088d8fa015'),
 ('3', '17', 'en_us', 'Storage', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-22 21:54:22', '2017-02-22 23:05:26', '6a7a17ef-6f49-49ac-98db-a7398a492fdc'),
 ('4', '18', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, '<p>One of the largest pieces of overhead involved in hosting a website is data storage - and media assets make up a large part of that. Storing gigabytes of photography, video, and graphics on your web host can make it difficult to move, backup, or deploy your site because it makes it heavier (figuratively). Offloading your media files to the cloud allows you to keep your web server thin while maintaining a central repository to manage your digital assets.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-22 21:54:22', '2017-02-22 23:05:26', '6ed35278-0748-4108-a6ee-391af9b8b4d4'),
 ('5', '19', 'en_us', 'Speed', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-22 21:54:22', '2017-02-22 23:05:26', '041504a1-aa78-4b00-a85f-aee798eb6846'),
 ('6', '20', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, '<p>Amazon\'s servers are low-latency and have incredibly fast transfer speeds which allow for quick rendering. With the added bonuses of using a <a href=\"http://www.sitepoint.com/7-reasons-to-use-a-cdn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Content Delivery Network (CDN)</a> such as caching and utilizing parallel downloads, you\'ll notice a huge difference in how fast your files show up on your page.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-22 21:54:22', '2017-02-22 23:05:26', '15fe12cb-583a-4dd7-ae48-361d8cb0a485'),
 ('7', '21', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'That\'s me', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-22 23:05:26', '2017-02-22 23:05:26', '778f80d1-2b3e-4c7d-9b94-f2504c0c412e'),
 ('8', '22', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This is a quote in a quote block. To call attention to a specific phrases or sentence.', 'Ryan Hall', '2017-02-22 23:05:26', '2017-02-22 23:05:26', 'f7fc4ed3-9e4b-40ec-9bf7-c45e374906f0'),
